{"tid":1672543,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"《蘋果》專題網站分清「假黃真藍」","createTime":"2019-10-24T07:19:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-26T06:55:58.000Z","uid":315584,"like":103,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":72,"replies":[{"pid":"56de9e51fff32b60c769cc2b5ad71fa00197a89b","tid":1672543,"uid":315584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T07:19:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CzN9SHa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCzN9SHa.jpg&h=49905156&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n歷時逾4個月的反送中運動，由議會內抗爭到議會外，多月的街頭活動後，抗爭平台再延伸至區議會。無論食肆、商店均出現「假黃」，為求得到大多數支持運動的香港人的認同，當然區議會選舉也不例外，有人標榜自己「年青」，「為香港帶來改變」；有人一句「香港人加油」，圖撇清與親建制團體的關係，面目模糊得容易讓人混淆。距離11月24日區議會選舉尚餘一個月，《蘋果》製作「2019區選光復香港」專題網站 ，讓你了解參選人的真正取態，他能否真正的代表到你，於區議會中為市民發聲，而不是繼續淪為「橡皮圖章」。<br />\n<br />\n報導LINK: <a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20191024/60185842\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191024%2F60185842&d=pzn6Hq8jxzH2PmSSbZvUobQTYXQauqfU4Ix09hrgZFI%3D&h=24a4df40\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191024%2F60185842&h=74761410\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20191024/60185842</a><br />\n<br />\n「2019區選光復香港」專題網站:<br />\n<a href=\"https://dce2019.appledaily.com/?fromSource=App&amp;type=mobile&amp;utm_campaign=hkad_201910_dce2019&amp;utm_medium=internal&amp;utm_source=hkad&amp;utm_content=article_inline&amp;_branch_match_id=715812173809717222\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdce2019.appledaily.com%2F%3FfromSource%3DApp%26type%3Dmobile%26utm_campaign%3Dhkad_201910_dce2019%26utm_medium%3Dinternal%26utm_source%3Dhkad%26utm_content%3Darticle_inline%26_branch_match_id%3D715812173809717222&d=pzn6Hq8jxzH2PmSSbZvUobQTYXQauqfU4Ix09hrgZFI%3D&h=aa07b32b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdce2019.appledaily.com%2F%3